snippet.title: A PSYCHO’S PATH | Can the Police Stop Him Before It Happens Again? | Full Movie
snippet.description:
A quiet desert town is shaken by a growing sense of fear.
Stopping what’s coming next becomes a race against time.

A remote California desert town is unsettled by a series of unexplained crimes carried out by a lone individual moving without a clear motive. With pressure mounting, Captain Peters and his understaffed police force launch an urgent manhunt across empty roads and isolated streets. As the search tightens, the challenge becomes finding the suspect before the town is pushed beyond its breaking point.

Director: Rocky Costanzo
Cast: Quinton “Rampage” Jackson, Steve De Forest, Noel Gugliemi.
